<div dir="ltr"><div>Hi Lorenzo,<br><br><span name="Lorenzo Donà" class=""></span><span name="Lorenzo Donà" class=""></span></div>I think you should  export the following before doing configuration step:<br><p>$ export F77=gfortran</p>


<p>$ export FFLAGS=&#39;-m64&#39;</p>

<p>$ export FC=gfortran</p>

<p>$ export FCFLAGS=&#39;-m64&#39;</p><p>Also include  --enable-gfortran  in the configure step line.</p><p>Yours,</p><p>Reem<br></p><br></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><br><div class="gmail_quote">On 19 June 2013 21:11, Lorenzo Donà <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:lorechimica91@hotmail.it" target="_blank">lorechimica91@hotmail.it</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>
